    communityinfo: "Community & Information",
    descCommunityInfo: "This section is designed to make essential legal, civic, and community information more accessible and easier to navigate. Systems that affect everyday life---from legal processes to housing support---are often complex and difficult to understand, especially for immigrant and underserved communities.",
    moreDesc: "To support clarity and access, this hub is organized into three focused sections. Each dropdown below helps users quickly find reliable information, verified resources, and community-centered initiatives.",
